!! Node properties

|!Property |!Type |!Default |!Notes |
|`label` |string | |Display text below node |
|`color` |color | |Background color |
|`fontColor` |color |auto |Text color (auto-derived from background contrast) |
|`borderColor` |color | |Border color |
|`borderWidth` |number |1 |Border thickness |
|`size` |number |25 |Node radius (Cytoscape renders at size × 2) |
|`shape` |enum |dot |`dot`/`box`/`ellipse`/`circle`/`diamond`/`triangle`/`star`/`hexagon`/`database` |
|`fixed` |boolean |false |Lock node position |
|`image` |image | |Background image |
|`cluster` |string | |ID of parent node for compound grouping (Cytoscape-only) |

!! Edge properties

|!Property |!Type |!Default |!Notes |
|`label` |string | |Text on edge (auto-rotated) |
|`color` |color | |Line and arrow color |
|`width` |number |1 |Line thickness |
|`arrows` |enum |to |`no`/`to`/`from`/`middle` (supports multiple) |
|`stroke` |enum |solid |`solid`/`dashed`/`dotted` |
|`hidden` |boolean |false |Hide edge |

!! Graph properties

|!Property |!Type |!Default |!Notes |
|`physics` |boolean |true |Enable COSE physics layout |
|`hierarchy` |boolean |false |Hierarchical layout |
|`hierarchyDirection` |enum |UD |`UD`/`DU`/`LR`/`RL` |
|`zoom` |boolean |true |Enable mouse wheel zoom |
|`zoomSpeed` |number |1 |Zoom sensitivity (0–10) |
|`navigation` |boolean |true |Enable panning |
|`nodeColor` |color | |Default node color |
|`edgeColor` |color | |Default edge color |
|`fontColor` |color | |Default text color |

!! Shape mapping

|!tw-graph |!Cytoscape |
|`dot` |`ellipse` |
|`circle` |`ellipse` |
|`ellipse` |`ellipse` |
|`box` |`rectangle` |
|`square` |`rectangle` |
|`diamond` |`diamond` |
|`triangle` |`triangle` |
|`star` |`star` |
|`hexagon` |`hexagon` |
|`database` |`barrel` |

!! Engine selection

Set `$:/config/flibbles/graph/engine` to `Cytoscape` or use the tw-graph settings UI.

</$fill>
